1. Installed nvm using curl command:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Exited terminal and reopened it.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0 using:
   nvm install 20.16.0
   nvm use 20.16.0

4. Verified installation with:
   node -v

5. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4
